    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. This example exhibits excellent mechanical health, with the individual throttle bodies providing instantaneous response and the double-VANOS system operating smoothly across the powerband. Crucial preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and throttle valve actuator service, has already been performed. The chassis retains its composure via Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a factory M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution during spirited cornering. While showing minor aesthetic wear consistent with its mileage, the subframe and suspension bushings remain tight, offering the pure hydraulic steering feedback enthusiasts crave. A mechanically sound, high-performance coupe ready for the canyon or the track.",
