    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with practicality. The exterior paint retains a deep gloss, though upon close inspection, you will notice minor road-wear such as small stone chips on the hood and a light scuff on the rear bumper. The alloy wheels are straight, with only a hint of curb rash on the front right. Inside, the cabin remains a comfortable sanctuary; the upholstery is free of tears or stains, showing only natural softening of the leather on the driver's seat bolster. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system, functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean and dry, reflecting a consistent maintenance schedule. It starts instantly, idles smoothly, and provides plenty of power on the highway. The transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains quiet over bumps. With recent brake service and tires that still have significant life left, this car is ready to go without any immediate investment required.",
